Insider Activity


Individual




Pen Yuen Wu



Dr. Wupen Yuen is Senior VP-Product & Technology Development at NeoPhotonics Corp. and VP-Product Development & Engineering at Neophotonics (China) Co. Ltd.
Dr. Yuen was previously employed as Chief Technology Officer by Bandwidth9, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from National Taiwan University, a graduate degree from Stanford University, and a doctorate degree from Stanford University.



