Note: Your Quotation Request will be directed to
                                        NeoPhotonics Corporation.
                                    






The PT-C88F3LECL from NeoPhotonics Corporation is a Fiber Optic Transceiver with Data Rate 400 Gb/s(8x50 Gb/s), Distance/Reach 10 km. More details for PT-C88F3LECL can be seen below.









