Pluggable Coherent Modules


The ClearLight™ CFP-DCO is a coherent pluggable module designed to support single-wavelength data transmission at 100G 
 


Coherent-Components


Enabling High Performance 100G to 400G and Beyond Coherent Transport
 
 


100G/400G Client Transceivers


Pluggable Modules Enabling 100G to 400G Client and Datacenter Connections
 
 


Optical Switching


Enabling Colorless, Directionless, Contentionless (CDC) ROADMs in High Speed Coherent Networks.
 
 


High Speed ICs


High Speed Drivers and Amplifiers Enable 100G/400G Transceivers
 
 


100G / 400G Laser Devices and Light Engines


Lasers and Modulators Enable 100G/400G Datacenter Transceivers
 
 


Passive Components


Passive Components Enable DWDM Network Connectivity
 
 


Network Monitoring and Control


Enabling Monitoring and Control of Optical Networks
 
 


10G and Low Rate Components


Lasers, Detectors and Drivers Enable Access Networks
 
 







































